                "DISNEY MOANA STYLING HEAD – The officially licensed Disney Princess styling head toy set features one of Disney’s most iconic princesses – Moana! The doll has Moana’s beautiful thick hair that is perfect for brushing, styling and practicing new hair styles on.",
